The people who left will tell you what the 
worst version or their version and it's  

1112
01:31:54,160 --> 01:31:57,480
on you to triangulate that 
information, but you need both sides.

1113
01:31:57,480 --> 01:32:01,920
Love that lesson. Bangaly, is there 
anything else that you want to share  

1114
01:32:01,920 --> 01:32:06,040
or leave listeners with before we get 
to our very exciting lightning round?

