1188
01:37:52,160 --> 01:37:56,000
time in all the right places. And that's 
really like ... It's a goal of mine. But  

1189
01:37:56,000 --> 01:38:04,080
the problem is that I don't ... My system 
for that specifically, I tend to ... I'm  

1190
01:38:04,080 --> 01:38:09,000
not rigorous with it is when I need to be.
But on the other hand, at work, I'm very  

1191
01:38:09,000 --> 01:38:15,240
